CHZZK
=====

This project is a personal fork/rework of the MIT-licensed upstream project:

- Upstream: bass9030/FUCK-CHZZK-GRID
- Upstream purpose: browser extension that bypasses CHZZK's NAVER Live Streaming Connector/grid-program requirement for high-quality playback
- Upstream license: MIT

The Chrome MV3 port by refracta/FUCK-CHZZK-GRID-CHROME was also used as a reference for Manifest V3 DNR behavior.

Local changes rename the project to CHZZK and change the behavior into a personal extension: no player-menu relabeling, no page script, no DOM dependency, and a static network-level redirect from lower CHZZK HLS playlist qualities to the highest target quality. The extension icon is CHZZK's official favicon from https://ssl.pstatic.net/static/nng/glive/icon/favicon.png.

The upstream MIT license text is preserved in LICENSE.
